2026-05-15T05:09:58.9374048Z 20-->/home/runner/work/prismTask/prismTask/app/build/intermediates/tmp/manifest/test/debug/tempFile2ProcessTestManifest1150817197014972422.xml:21:22-78
2026-05-15T05:09:58.9374138Z 21    <!--
2026-05-15T05:09:58.9374351Z 22        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-15T05:09:58.9374466Z 23        across Android versions:
2026-05-15T05:09:58.9374669Z 24          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-15T05:09:58.9374853Z 25            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-15T05:09:58.9375205Z 26            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-15T05:09:58.9375391Z 27          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-15T05:09:58.9375601Z 28            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-15T05:09:58.9375804Z 29        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-15T05:09:58.9375990Z 30        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-15T05:09:58.9376153Z 31        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-15T05:09:58.9376246Z 32    -->
